Pre-Game Insights: A Malian refereeing quartet led by Boubou Traore has arrived in Garoua to officiate the Cameroon vs Namibia AFCON qualifier on September 7, 2024.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The referees are set to commence training on September 5, 2024, to familiarize themselves with the playing venue.
Others: Cameroon's national team is expected to arrive in Garoua on Thursday, while Namibia is scheduled to land later that night.
